overview: A corrupt business man, Richard J. Slip, plans on demolishing an orphanage to make way for his new shopping mall. Now it's up to SuperDawg, with the aid of hip friends, to stop Slip and his army of ninja cops.
tagline: Can Richard Slip be stopped? Can SuperDawg save the kids? Are you ready for the FINAL SUPERDAWG ADVENTURE?
title: SuperDawg 3: SuperDawg Saves the Kids
